                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6100" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0936</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10076 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“守门人”失责：康美药业审计难言“康美”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Gatekeeper’s blame: it is hard to say that the audits of Kangmei Pharmaceutical Co. have fulfilled their obligation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒲丹琳，夏尧，赵菁莹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东正中珠江会计师事务所</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务舞弊；审计程序；注册会计师</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial fraud; Audit procedures; Certified Public Accountant</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">审计作为资本市场的“守门人”，对于资本市场的正常运转至关重要。近年来财务舞弊案件频发，尤其是2019年康美药业坐实A股最大财务造假案，受到证监会处罚。与此同时，作为康美药业的审计机构，广东正中珠江会计师事务所因此受到“株连”，被证监会立案调查。在证监会对正中珠江的审计过程进行抽丝剥茧后，诸多潜在的审计问题开始浮出水面。本案例回顾了康美药业财务造假案件的发展历程，并通过对正中珠江会计师事务所的审计过程进行分析，引导学员结合理论知识，思考正中珠江会计师事务所在审计的过程中存在的问题是什么，是否符合审计准则规范，使学员对现代风险导向审计理论能够有更深一步理解，进而提升学员的实践应用能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the &quot;gatekeeper&quot; of the capital market, auditing is essential to the normal operation of the capital market. In recent years, there have been frequent cases of financial fraud, especially the largest financial fraud case of Kangmei Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. in 2019, which was punished by the China Securities Regulatory Commission. At the same time, as the audit agency of Kangmei Pharmaceutical, Guangdong BP Certified Public Accountants was &quot;linked&quot; and was investigated by the Securities Regulatory Commission. After the China Securities Regulatory Commission conducted a decoupling of the audit process of the BP Pearl River, many potential audit problems began to surface. This case reviews the development process of Kangmei Pharmaceutical’s financial fraud case, and analyzes the audit process of BP Certified Public Accountants, and guides the students to combine theoretical knowledge and think about the problems that exist in the audit process of BP Certified Public Accountants. , Whether it conforms to the audit standards and regulations, so that the students can have a deeper understanding of modern risk-oriented audit theory, and then enhance the students&#39; practical application ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险导向审计理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
